OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1779451869
OL,3,CPep Guardiola's emotional goodbye
OL,4,Cmessage in full
OL,6,FManchester City have confirmed that
OL,7,FPep Guardiola will step down as
OL,8,Fmanager this summer.
OL,10,FThe Catalan, who joined the club in
OL,11,FJuly 2016, will leave having won 20
OL,12,Fmajor trophies - making him the most
OL,13,Fsuccessful manager in City's history.
OL,15,FIn an emotional message to fans, Pep
OL,16,Fpaid tribute to the city of Manchester.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/7
