OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1779451869
OL,3,CPep Guardiola's emotional goodbye
OL,4,Cmessage in full
OL,6,FHe said: "And what a time we have had
OL,7,Ftogether. Don't ask me the reasons I'm
OL,8,Fleaving. There is no reason, but deep
OL,9,Finside, I know it's my time. Nothing
OL,10,Fis eternal, if it was, I would be
OL,11,Fhere. Eternal will be the feeling, the
OL,12,Fpeople, the memories, the love I have
OL,13,Ffor my Manchester City.
OL,26,@nD@JOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,394,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1779451869
OL,3,CPep Guardiola's emotional goodbye
OL,4,Cmessage in full
OL,6,F"This is a city built from work. From
OL,7,Fgraft. You see it in the colour of the
OL,8,Fbricks. From people who clocked in
OL,9,Fearly, stayed late. The factories. The
OL,10,FPankhursts. The unions. The music.
OL,11,FSimply the Industrial Revolution and
OL,12,Fhow this changed the world. And I
OL,13,Fthink I grew to understand that, and
OL,14,Fmy teams did too.
OL,16,F"We worked. We suffered. We fought.
OL,17,FAnd we did things our own way. Our way.
OL,26,@nD@AOUxD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,394,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1779451869
OL,3,CPep Guardiola's emotional goodbye
OL,4,Cmessage in full
OL,6,F"Hard work comes in many forms. Trips
OL,7,Fto Bournemouth, when we lost the
OL,8,FPremier League, and you were there.
OL,9,FTrips to Istanbul, when you were
OL,10,Fthere, too.
OL,12,F"Remember, the Manchester Arena
OL,13,Fattack, when this city showed the
OL,14,Fworld what strength actually looks
OL,15,Flike? Not anger. Not fear. Just love.
OL,16,FCommunity. Togetherness. A city united.
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,394,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1779451869
OL,3,CPep Guardiola's emotional goodbye
OL,4,Cmessage in full
OL,6,F"Remember, losing my mum during COVID
OL,7,Fand feeling this club carry me through
OL,8,Fit. The fans, the staff, the people of
OL,9,FManchester, you gave me strength when
OL,10,FI needed it most. Cris, my kids, my
OL,11,Fwhole family, you were there as
OL,12,Falways. Khaldoon, you were there too.
OL,14,F"Players don't forget - every single
OL,15,Finstant, moment, me, my staff, this
OL,16,Fclub, everything. What we have done,
OL,17,Fwe have done it for all of you. And
OL,18,Fyou have been just exceptional. You
OL,19,Fdon't know it yet, but you are leaving
OL,20,Fa legacy.
OL,26,@nD@AOUvD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,394,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39306
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1779451869
OL,3,CPep Guardiola's emotional goodbye
OL,4,Cmessage in full
OL,6,F"So as my time comes to an end, be
OL,7,Fhappy. Oasis are back again.
OL,9,F"Ladies and gentlemen, thank you for
OL,10,Ftrusting me.
OL,12,F"Thank you for pushing me.
OL,14,F"Thank you for loving me.
OL,16,F"Tony Walsh said in his unforgettable
OL,17,Fpoem this is the place. I'm sorry,
OL,18,FTony: this is my place.
OL,20,F"Noel...I was right.
OL,26,@nD@AOUqD@AOUtD@AOUvD@AOUxD@AOU|D@AOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
